{"has_more_entries": true, "subscriptions": "", "error": "", "posts": [{"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBlxQxXC", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 14, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8714796, "raw_content": "I always feel like people living in the suburbs who act like the suburbs are some kind of hell on Earth are among the most spoiled and ungrateful people out there. Its like \"oh no, everybody's got a big yard and a big house and they're all families, and there's low crime, and we've all got cars... I'm so miserable!\"\n\nIts like, how spoiled do you have to be to think the suburbs are some kind of terrible place? I mean, I get it if you live in the kind of crappy suburb that is almost like half-urban, half suburb instead of really being a suburb. But usually the people whining about suburbs are people who live in the really nice, sheltered suburbs.\n\nEven if a suburb is \"cookie cutter.\" I still feel like suburban life is just inherently nice.", "author": "MAGA9428", "created": 1783279561282, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "love_laugh_prey", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Pet Peeve of Mine: People Who Whine About Suburbs...", "last_comment_created": 1783285051422, "content": "<p>I always feel like people living in the suburbs who act like the suburbs are some kind of hell on Earth are among the most spoiled and ungrateful people out there. Its like &quot;oh no, everybody's got a big yard and a big house and they're all families, and there's low crime, and we've all got cars... I'm so miserable!&quot;</p>\n<p>Its like, how spoiled do you have to be to think the suburbs are some kind of terrible place? I mean, I get it if you live in the kind of crappy suburb that is almost like half-urban, half suburb instead of really being a suburb. But usually the people whining about suburbs are people who live in the really nice, sheltered suburbs.</p>\n<p>Even if a suburb is &quot;cookie cutter.&quot; I still feel like suburban life is just inherently nice.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 14, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2073258346317230179", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlxQP2M", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 27, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8714536, "raw_content": "", "author": "kinbergfan", "created": 1783266642362, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DeepStateParasite", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBlxQP2M.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/xhnews/status/2073258346317230179?s=46", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "The CCP Hates America \n\n", "last_comment_created": 1783275222199, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 27, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 138, "created": 1783138283000, 